# Test Images Directory

Place test document images here for evaluation.

## Serving Images Locally

Start a simple HTTP server:

```bash
cd test_images
python -m http.server 8080
```

Images will be accessible at: http://localhost:8080/filename.png

## Recommended Test Images

- bank_statement_good.png
- bank_statement_blurry.png
- bank_statement_skewed.png
- w2_good.png
- w2_blurry.png
- 1099_int_good.png

## Creating Degraded Test Images

Use ImageMagick to create test variants:

```bash
# Blur
convert original.png -blur 0x3 blurry.png

# Skew
convert original.png -rotate 15 skewed.png

# Low contrast
convert original.png -brightness-contrast -20x-30 lowcontrast.png
```
